Vila Gesel, Argentina

183
00:22:31,505 --> 00:22:34,241
(Dobar dan, gospodo!
-Dobar dan!)

184
00:22:34,398 --> 00:22:35,900
(Vruće je, zar ne?
-Da.)

185
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:38,538
(Pivo, molim.)

186
